<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM13.7">
<l>veṟṟik karuḷa koṭiyāṉṟaṉ mīmī tāṭā vulakattu</l>
<l>veṟṟa veṟitē peṟṟatāy vēmpē yāka vaḷarttāḷē</l>
<l>kuṟṟa maṟṟa mulai taṉṉaik kumaraṉ kōlap paṇaittōḷō</l>
<l>ṭaṟṟa kuṟṟa mavaitīra vaṇaiya vamukkik kaṭṭīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Yaśodā] begot Him for absolutely no use, and brought Him up like neem</l>
<l>in this world that moves based on the greatness of He whose banner</l>
<l rend="indent">is the victorious Garuḍa!</l>
<l>Press and bind [my] flawless breasts  with the handsome palm[-like] shoulders</l>
<l>Of the young Man so that the distress of [His] severing [ties with me] end!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
